summary: ...OCTAVE WEAKENS SLIGHTLY AND CONTINUES WEST-NORTHWESTWARD... As of 2:00 AM PDT Fri Oct 03 the center of Octave was located near 13.1, -120.4 with movement WNW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1001 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
